<item>
            <title>[MAHOUT-634] Need more online averagers</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-634</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I am occasionally seeing a need to do exponential averaging of values or rates.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hbase guys want this as well.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So it is time to do it.  I have a patch that does the averaging of values according to&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://tdunning.blogspot.com/2011/03/exponential-weighted-averages-with.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://tdunning.blogspot.com/2011/03/exponential-weighted-averages-with.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will attach that as a patch now and do the rate averaging as well before committing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
